      <title>投资者权衡风险，欧洲股市在美国数据公布前下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/european-stocks-edge-higher-ahead-of-us-data-gsk-shares-jump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者等待美国关键通胀数据，并关注地缘政治发展，欧洲股市周四小幅走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/european-stocks-edge-higher-ahead-of-us-data-gsk-shares-jump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 07:16:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
